<br>
 I have 2 PSUs and I basically use them for the stats now more then anything else.<br>
<br>
 I don't have the plat to buy these weapons that inflict alot of damage on every hit. I saw a SOS this past weekend and the guy wanted 5K minimum.<br>
<br>
